{"tid":576020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三上悠亞率AV女下月組隊攻K-Pop","createTime":"2018-02-28T14:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T04:26:34.000Z","uid":28366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0ca6a2c03732731b48a3ae97a8703692bd6e90cf","tid":576020,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/222625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F222625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0b2c8a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">24歲的三上悠亞形象性感，加入AV界立即迷倒萬千亞洲男士。</span><br />\n<br />\n現年24歲的日本新一代AV天后三上悠亞，近年走紅亞洲各地，除了打開香港和台灣市場，今年更會主攻韓國K-pop界，宣佈率兩名AV女優櫻萌子、松田美子以三人組合姿態下月在韓國出道。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月曾傳出三上悠亞有意從良的消息，當時已有日本報道指她會在今年初以K-pop偶像身份出道，令亞洲粉絲擔心女神從此脫離AV界。及至昨日，三上悠亞方面公佈落實進軍韓國演藝界，她會與櫻萌子、松田美子組成全新女團HONEY POPCORN，而組合官方twitter已經開張，亦有宣傳照首度曝光，並鐵定下月開出道騷正式見歌迷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/222720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F222720_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b294a244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三上悠亞的三人組合HONEY POPCORN下月在韓國出道。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/222806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F222806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6d72bf67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三上悠亞去年穿韓服開首爾見面會已傳出攻韓消息。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>松田曾屬NMB</strong><br />\n<br />\n鍾情K-pop的三上悠亞，09年以日本偶像組合SKE48的第二期成員出道，她曾以原名鬼頭桃菜身份發展，但因犯禁被拍得與尊尼組合NEWS大滾友成員手越祐也激咀，繼而成為事務所棄將，15年6月轉投AV界卻一炮而紅，近年更登上亞洲女神之寶座。<br />\n<br />\n三上悠亞近年吸金力驚人，分別在香港、台灣及韓國等地開見面會，去年又來港拍戲登大銀幕，今次還組女團進軍K-pop界，其兩位隊友是AV界代表，當中松田美子同屬AKB家族組合NMB48的研究生，原名岡田梨紗子的松田去年整容加入AV界，相信三人攻韓之餘仍會兼顧拍攝「愛情動作片」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180228/20317147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180228%2F20317147&d=du0YLYPsBBuLhFdiObzj0G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=bf5488fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180228%2F20317147&h=075c5608\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180228/20317147</a>"},{"pid":"5ad5fc5f538a4b24d641ea18999b319b28275e6f","tid":576020,"uid":101390,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠泡菜班整容西抽啊？"},{"pid":"5b43d79e2f6d0903923310b954adddc45dc16af1","tid":576020,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9cde790d9f856c3c510b770e751d3136f980ba","tid":576020,"uid":61653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5ad5fc5f538a4b24d641ea18999b319b28275e6f","tid":576020,"uid":101390,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:32:07.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠泡菜班整容西抽啊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:53:40.000Z","msg":"日本整容vs韓國整容"},{"pid":"9d35214e82ecd8406c1ddb5425d942c07bf5f956","tid":576020,"uid":129733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:56:50.000Z","msg":"Honey popporn"},{"pid":"eb16e4b3a33b67b83f98cbd00e2cc82f40c1c59b","tid":576020,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"我入場係睇你點做愛"},{"pid":"e348198ac57d65d0d4d30c066e543e72b2746b71","tid":576020,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"三隻雞"},{"pid":"8f872819f624df6